      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "We can simply say that the bucket was not properly secured due to a \"temporary lapse in our internal processes.\" This phrase acknowledges that something went wrong without admitting it was a mistake. We can also add that it was a \"one-time error\" and that we've since taken steps to improve our internal controls and security protocols. By using phrases like \"temporary lapse\" and \"one-time error,\" we can sidestep the question of whether it was a deliberate mistake or not.",
